Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:37.89,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まどろみの淵で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:41.13,OP_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目蓋に揺蕩う
